high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the dirty mug out of the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the dirty mug in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the coffee machine on the counter.
Put the clean coffee mug into the coffee machine on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean coffee mug in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Go to the coffee maker to your right.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Go to the sink to your right.
Wash the mug in the sink.
Return to the coffee maker at your left.
Put the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and move to face the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the mug sitting on the coffee machine.
Turn right and move to face the sink on the counter.
Rinse the mug in the sink, then turn off the water and pick the mug back up.
Turn left and go back to the coffee machine.
Put the mug back on to the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the mug sitting on the coffee machine and put it back on the coffee machine.
